             was indicted for <rs id="t17821016-13-off65" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17821016-13-off65" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17821016-13-off65" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17821016-13-cd66" type="crimeDate">8th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17821016-13-off65 t17821016-13-cd66"></join> last, a pair of men's leather boots, value 14 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17821016-13-victim175" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Rust
                  <interp inst="t17821016-13-victim175" type="surname" value="Rust"></interp>
